When is array required?

::::multiple values+ same data type+ defined size of the array::::



--> Collection of homegenous data
--> Group of multiple values of same data type with fixed size
--> Contains duplicate data
--> Data stored on the basis of index; index starts from 0
--> Random access
--> Contiguous Memory Allocation
--> Array is treated as object in java


----Syntax:
        data_type array_name[] = new data_type[size];


